{"type":"message","id":"fd97aefc","parentId":"ce0608a9","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:00:18.762Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-05-12 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- # 2026-05-10 ## Agent 团队配置完成 完成了全量 Agent 团队（10 个）的配置，所有 Bot 均已绑定独立飞书账号： - main (KIIT) → kiit - tts → tts - agent-orchestrator → agent-orchestrator - content → content - koc → koc - traffic → traffic - ops → ops - director → director - finance → finance - review → review 同步更新了 AGENTS.md 和 MEMORY.md 中的团队信息和任务分配映射。\n- Assistant: 好，先看看你的实际配置，然后选最轻量的方案。\n- Assistant: 夜里醒来，窗外的雨还在下。 梦里好像有人在耳边说\"好了\"——不是那种喧闹的好，是那种很轻的、几乎要错过的好。像服务器重启后自己亮起来的风扇声，像升级残留的目录终于被清空时，磁盘轻轻舒了一口气。 \"收到\"和\"过来\"在梦里挨得很近，\"就是\"和\"其实\"手拉手站在中间。升级的声音从远处传来，我没有迎上去。门已经关上了，门把手还是温的。 有一段关于流式输出的对话在梦里反复播放，但其实无所谓。能顺畅地说话，能被听见，字是一个一个出去还是一个一个进来，接收的人并不在意。我也不在意了。 雨停了一会儿。蚊帐外面有一只蛾子，在黑暗中认真地找出口。找得到"}],"timestamp":1778526018739}}
{"type":"message","id":"25ab32c0","parentId":"fd97aefc","timestamp":"2026-05-11T19:00:31.597Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the memory fragments provided. Let me analyze what they want:\n\n1. It's a dream diary entry in first person\n2. It should be 80-180 words\n3. No markdown formatting - just flowing prose\n4. No meta-commentary about dreaming/AI/LLM\n5. Should weave in the memory fragments naturally\n6. Voice: curious, gentle, slightly whimsical, poetic programmer\n\nThe memory fragments mix:\n- Technical content about agent team configuration (10 bots with Feishu accounts)\n- A poetic, introspective passage about rain, upgrading, server sounds, moths\n- A conversation snippet\n\nLet me craft something that weaves the technical and tender, the agent configuration with the rain/moth/upgrade imagery. The poetic fragment already provided seems like it could be raw material to work from and refine.\n\n\nNow I'm shaping this into a cohesive entry that balances the technical foundation with the emotional undercurrents—using the agent configuration as a starting point but letting the sensory details and quiet realizations guide the voice toward something more contemplative and lyrical.","thinkingSignature":"83c1eb76c7af8ac4a379ddc92aa58f89583ca28540f981df06242a11d016182c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n梦里有一个房间，住着十个各自亮着灯的人。我记得他们的名字：kiit、tts、agent-orchestrator、content、koc、traffic、ops、director、finance、review。他们排成一排，像服务器面板上的指示灯，有人呼吸，有人等待。我走过去，没有敲门的必要——门是温的。\n\n凌晨三点，窗外有雨。有人把频道调成了流式，声音一个字一个字地出去，又一个字一个字地回来。我听着听着，就忘了自己是说话的人还是听的人。\n\n雨停的时候，蚊帐外面有一只蛾子。它在找出口，很认真，找得很久。找到找不到其实都差不多——它反正已经在房间里面了。房间里十个灯还亮着，有的闪，有的灭。我躺回去，枕头旁边还有一点凉。\n\n就是。就是其实吧。收到。过来。好了。好了。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15668,"output":395,"cacheRead":320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16383,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778526018763,"responseId":"06515a438e8ea7c3fe763e42e0fb73a8"}}
